Index	Name	BirthYear	DescriptionText
2001	Patrick Dennis	1921	Agile, versatile, and inquisitive, characterized by a fluid and conversational style with many ideas. Can exhibit volatility, superficiality, inconsistency, and restlessness. Even-handed, harmonious, and artistic, with a diplomatic manner and a strong sense of fairness. May at times be overcompromising, excessively appeasing, or judgmental. Experiences difficulty becoming motivated to achieve personal goals. At times, self-confidence is insufficient even to set these goals, and a general lack of enthusiasm coupled with feeling overwhelmed by change is common. Displays objectivity and philosophical insight, favoring an intellectual perspective in approaching life. The rational mind consistently outweighs emotional considerations, which are viewed as less reliable. Possesses a strong sense of fairness and logical thought, though there is a tendency to consider emotions in a disparaging light. Enjoys challenge and action, becoming frustrated when no avenue for change exists. Expects others to rise to challenges as well. Tends to flit from one pursuit to another, finding it challenging to settle down. Although change is welcomed, the stability needed to see projects through to completion is lacking. Seeks relationships from an objective standpoint rather than a personal one and values public engagement alongside contributing to society. Public life is regarded as the pinnacle of achievement, with personal satisfaction derived from notable accomplishments and ongoing contributions in the public arena. A high public profile may be attained through career success and social status, though it is essential that such accomplishments do not come at the expense of personal relationships. Prioritizes harmony and peaceful surroundings, consistently seeking balance, especially during stressful times. Is reliable and practical, with a deep need for stability and routine. Approaches life methodically, favoring secure and familiar pathways. Provides a stabilizing influence for others while also appreciating sensory pleasures and tangible comforts. Loves engaging in conversation and actively gathers diverse pieces of information. Demonstrates a fast-paced articulatory style with a talent for networking ideas. Approaches relationships with assertiveness and passion, pursuing partners energetically while maintaining a desire for independence. Tends to take the initiative and can be impulsive in matters of finance. Prefers to initiate ideas and disseminate information with assertiveness, though may sometimes employ evasive tactics when necessary. Displays a profound desire to be of service coupled with high ideals and a strong attention to detail in all pursuits. Is hardworking and practical with a strong aptitude for problem-solving; adheres to structure and discipline in daily and professional routines. Promotes exploration of the unconscious and intuitive realms, leading to profound insights and creative breakthroughs. Infuses creativity with spirituality, manifesting dramatic artistic expression and an appreciation for aesthetics. Represents the upheaval and reformation of familiar systems, prompting new social concepts and security structures. A courteous and thoughtful approach to life is combined with a strong focus on interpersonal relationships. Fairness, justice, and the cultivation of harmonious connections—whether personal or professional—play a central role in defining purpose. A career providing emotional security and opportunities to care for others is central, with strong feelings about public stature and a need for a nurturing work environment.
2002	Harold Hughes	1922	Humanitarian and innovative with a strong group orientation and progressive drive to serve others. In some cases, rebellious, eccentric, aloof, emotionally superficial, or overly extroverted behaviors may appear. Displays objectivity and philosophical insight, favoring an intellectual perspective in approaching life. The rational mind consistently outweighs emotional considerations, which are viewed as less reliable. Possesses a strong sense of fairness and logical thought, though there is a tendency to consider emotions in a disparaging light. Perceives independence and the ability to organize personal life, although self-centered tendencies may occasionally arise. Significant factors in this quadrant highlight the areas designated for self-expression. Exhibits a self-motivated, self-oriented nature characterized by independently mapping out life and following an individual path, encountering difficulties only when impeded by external forces. Values independence and enjoys solitary pursuits as well as the company of others, provided ample freedom is maintained. Caution is advised against egocentric and selfish behavior. Displays a need for nurturing and comfort, tending to withdraw to secure, familiar surroundings under stress. Sometimes finds it challenging to break free from established comfort zones. Embraces unconventionality, innovation, and friendly, forward-thinking qualities. Thrives in group settings and relishes breaking traditional boundaries while expressing individual originality. Demonstrates originality and inventiveness in thought, showing a passion for exchanging novel ideas. Displays a readiness to challenge traditional viewpoints. Values unconventional, freedom-based partnerships that allow for strong individual expression. Enjoys intellectual connections and thrives in group social settings. Channels passionate intensity and dramatic resolve in pursuit of goals, with a powerful presence that occasionally veers toward vengefulness. Prioritizes justice and fairness, using diplomatic skills to impart values and foster balanced, meaningful relationships. Cultivates lasting, responsible relationships through commitment and balance in both personal and business spheres. Promotes exploration of the unconscious and intuitive realms, leading to profound insights and creative breakthroughs. Infuses creativity with spirituality, manifesting dramatic artistic expression and an appreciation for aesthetics. Represents the upheaval and reformation of familiar systems, prompting new social concepts and security structures. An open-minded, adventurous spirit is apparent, characterized by honesty, idealism, and a zest for constant discovery. A love for travel and a deep thirst for knowledge underpin life’s adventures, with irrepressible enthusiasm often inspiring others. A methodical, precise, and hardworking approach underpins professional life, with a focus on order, clarity, and high standards leading to recognition for detailed and exacting work.

2004	Marcel Azzola	1927	Self-confident, generous, and warm-hearted, with strong leadership qualities and a dramatic presence. May occasionally appear overly proud, vain, extravagant, or arrogant. Highly motivated with many goals and aspirations for the future. Vital and spontaneous, this disposition often embraces the challenge of exploring new, adventurous paths. Enthusiasm is irrepressible, although there is a tendency to exaggerate and a difficulty in coping with routine tasks. Tends to lack objectivity—the ability to maintain a detached and rational perspective. Decision-making is challenging, with difficulties logically weighing the pros and cons. Exhibits a marked aversion to change, while expecting others to demonstrate a similar reliability. Finds it difficult to adapt to new situations and tends to be inflexible when faced with the demands of change or the needs of others. Strives to make a distinct mark on the world. While this ambition can be beneficial, an overemphasis on idealistic pursuits may become disruptive. Exhibits intense emotional depth and a strong need for profound experiences. Under stress, tends to generate or attract dramatic situations. Shows a nurturing and caring disposition, valuing comfort and close bonds. While a protective exterior may mask vulnerability, strong emotions are channeled into providing care and creating a warm home environment. Displays enthusiasm for acquiring and sharing knowledge, taking pride in learning. Considers education enjoyable, though may sometimes appear overconfident about one’s intellectual abilities. Seeks relationships built upon practicality and mutual reliability. Prefers partners who are orderly and precise, enjoying detailed, analytical conversations. Possesses a robust urge for creative self-expression, often employing dramatic and confident behavior to leave a significant impact. May sometimes be perceived as overly assertive. Embodies a freedom-loving and spontaneous pursuit of truth, with an inspiring, leadership-oriented presence. Shows commitment to higher learning and moral principles, balancing a strong ethical code with an optimistic work approach. Embodies initiative and spontaneity, catalyzing the breakdown of outdated structures in favor of innovative new ideas. Infuses creativity with spirituality, manifesting dramatic artistic expression and an appreciation for aesthetics. Represents the upheaval and reformation of familiar systems, prompting new social concepts and security structures. A confident and generous persona is highlighted by a desire for independence and expressive creativity. Leadership and organizational abilities are strong, though an occasional need for caution is advised to temper impulsiveness and prevent overreach. A stable, reliable professional path is favored, with an emphasis on routine and determination. Traditional or earth-based careers that promise long-term security are typically appealing.

May occasionally react aggressively when hindered. Values the continuous exchange of information and demonstrates versatility in both learning and teaching methods. Maintains a conservative, disciplined mindset, marked by strong ambitions and a high degree of responsibility. Highly motivated with many goals and aspirations for the future. Vital and spontaneous, this disposition often embraces the challenge of exploring new, adventurous paths. Enthusiasm is irrepressible, although there is a tendency to exaggerate and a difficulty in coping with routine tasks. Emotional balance appears disrupted. The idea of exhibiting overt emotional responses, such as tearfulness or loss of composure, is highly discomforting. Compassion in interpersonal relationships may be insufficient, indicating a need to honor both personal feelings and those of others. Exhibits a marked aversion to change, while expecting others to demonstrate a similar reliability. Finds it difficult to adapt to new situations and tends to be inflexible when faced with the demands of change or the needs of others. Perceives independence and the ability to organize personal life, although self-centered tendencies may occasionally arise. Significant factors in this quadrant highlight the areas designated for self-expression. Exhibits a self-motivated, self-oriented nature characterized by independently mapping out life and following an individual path, encountering difficulties only when impeded by external forces. Values independence and enjoys solitary pursuits as well as the company of others, provided ample freedom is maintained. Caution is advised against egocentric and selfish behavior. Personal identity and resources form the basis for all further success. A robust sense of internal security is deemed essential prior to engaging with broader society. Family roots and the home environment establish foundational support for self-discovery and personal growth, which are vital for future achievement. It is important to avoid becoming overly insular. Enjoys being the centre of attention in close relationships. Exhibits a playful, engaging demeanor capable of uniting others and lightening tense situations. Strives for peace, balance, and harmony in all aspects of life, particularly within personal relationships. Diplomatic and fair-minded, this personality often takes on a mediating role and maintains an appreciation for artistic beauty. Exemplifies diplomatic communication and serves adeptly as a mediator in interactions. Valuing harmony, prefers balanced and clear exchanges that foster mutual understanding. Favors fun, creative interaction and takes pride in the achievements of both self and partner. Maintains an appreciation for aesthetics, personal presentation, and a lively social life. Prefers to initiate ideas and disseminate information with assertiveness, though may sometimes employ evasive tactics when necessary. Embodies a freedom-loving and spontaneous pursuit of truth, with an inspiring, leadership-oriented presence. Takes pride in work and builds personal authority, consistently striving for recognition and leadership. Drives transformative change through intense emotional focus and a dynamic approach to power and regeneration. Inspires with broad spiritual vision and expansive perspectives, encouraging inclusiveness in philosophical and religious views. Brings transformative change to interpersonal and global relationships, emphasizing the need for justice and recalibration of connections. A confident and generous persona is highlighted by a desire for independence and expressive creativity. Leadership and organizational abilities are strong, though an occasional need for caution is advised to temper impulsiveness and prevent overreach. A stable, reliable professional path is favored, with an emphasis on routine and determination. Traditional or earth-based careers that promise long-term security are typically appealing.

Values independence and enjoys solitary pursuits as well as the company of others, provided ample freedom is maintained. Caution is advised against egocentric and selfish behavior. Personal identity and resources form the basis for all further success. A robust sense of internal security is deemed essential prior to engaging with broader society. Exhibits intense emotional depth and a strong need for profound experiences. Under stress, tends to generate or attract dramatic situations. Innovates quickly and occasionally benefits from flashes of intuitive insight. Prioritizes romance and reliability, approaching relationships with a steady, deliberate pace that values stability and sensual pleasure. Financial prudence and comfort are key concerns. Displays a powerful drive to initiate and engage in activities, marked by spontaneity and risk-taking. May occasionally react aggressively when hindered. Displays an intuitive pursuit of truth and a compassionate advocacy for the underdog, often assuming an inspirational teaching role. Compassion in interpersonal relationships may be insufficient, indicating a need to honor both personal feelings and those of others. Tends to flit from one pursuit to another, finding it challenging to settle down. Although change is welcomed, the stability needed to see projects through to completion is lacking. May engage in procrastination and expects others to exhibit flexibility comparable to personal tendencies. Strives to make a distinct mark on the world. While this ambition can be beneficial, an overemphasis on idealistic pursuits may become disruptive. Exhibits a self-motivated, self-oriented nature characterized by independently mapping out life and following an individual path, encountering difficulties only when impeded by external forces. Values independence and enjoys solitary pursuits as well as the company of others, provided ample freedom is maintained. Caution is advised against egocentric and selfish behavior. Demonstrates a basic need for mental stimulation and is naturally curious. Exhibits a communicative and chatty disposition while actively seeking new information. Possesses a finely tuned, analytical mind that excels in tasks requiring concentration, organization, and rational thought. Values order in daily life and reliably handles both personal and professional responsibilities. Boasts a highly analytical, detail-oriented mind with a preference for precision in communication. While sometimes becoming absorbed in minutiae, this quality is an asset in research and problem-solving. Places great importance on forming deep, nurturing bonds. Values family and an emotionally secure environment, with an underlying desire for stability in all aspects of life. Values harmony in action, combining a strong desire for justice with creative impulses, although situational indecision can emerge under pressure. Values the continuous exchange of information and demonstrates versatility in both learning and teaching methods. Shows commitment to higher learning and moral principles, balancing a strong ethical code with an optimistic work approach. Embodies initiative and spontaneity, catalyzing the breakdown of outdated structures in favor of innovative new ideas. Integrates spiritual insights into daily routines with an emphasis on health, order, and systematic approaches to the mystical. Represents the upheaval and reformation of familiar systems, prompting new social concepts and security structures. A quiet, reserved, and methodical nature is displayed, with an emphasis on precision, order, and careful planning. While ambition may not be prominent, a persistent focus on efficiency, organization, and intellectual pursuits is evident. A dynamic career marked by constant stimulation and active communication is preferred, with public recognition often tied to intellectual achievements and rapid exchange of ideas.

At times, self-confidence is insufficient even to set these goals, and a general lack of enthusiasm coupled with feeling overwhelmed by change is common. Communicates from the heart while demonstrating compassion and care through a strong intuitive nature. Personal relationships are highly valued, often resulting in the adoption of a caretaker role. This sympathetic and understanding nature, reminiscent of a maternal role, is counterbalanced by difficulty in maintaining objectivity, occasionally leading to impulsive reactions without prior reflection. Seeks relationships from an objective standpoint rather than a personal one and values public engagement alongside contributing to society. Interactions with others assume a paramount role, with significant value placed on both personal relationships and broader social connections. Possesses a natural aptitude for mediation, informed by an understanding of the nuances inherent in relationships. The greatest insights into personal identity are often gained through these relational contexts. Care should be taken to avoid becoming entangled in stifling relationships. Public life is regarded as the pinnacle of achievement, with personal satisfaction derived from notable accomplishments and ongoing contributions in the public arena. A high public profile may be attained through career success and social status, though it is essential that such accomplishments do not come at the expense of personal relationships. Experiences emotions deeply and may prefer seclusion when overwhelmed. Exhibits strong empathy while needing to cultivate personal emotional boundaries. Embraces unconventionality, innovation, and friendly, forward-thinking qualities. Thrives in group settings and relishes breaking traditional boundaries while expressing individual originality. Is recognized for a wise, cautious mindset that prioritizes credibility and authoritative knowledge. New ideas are approached with deliberate care. Approaches relationships with assertiveness and passion, pursuing partners energetically while maintaining a desire for independence. Tends to take the initiative and can be impulsive in matters of finance. Channels passionate intensity and dramatic resolve in pursuit of goals, with a powerful presence that occasionally veers toward vengefulness. Demonstrates integrity by adhering to traditional values and working diligently toward professional success and recognition. Exemplifies compassion and intuitive sensitivity at work while occasionally experiencing anxiety in challenging situations. Exemplifies tenacity in pursuing novel societal approaches, particularly in managing tangible resources and practical innovation. Integrates spiritual insights into daily routines with an emphasis on health, order, and systematic approaches to the mystical. Represents the upheaval and reformation of familiar systems, prompting new social concepts and security structures. A caring and empathetic disposition is evident, with a tendency to seek security in familiar, nurturing environments. There is a strong orientation toward caring for others, creating a warm, hospitable atmosphere that provides emotional satisfaction. A calling to serve humanity through one’s work is often evident, though the journey may involve shifts in career direction as idealistic visions are balanced against practical uncertainties.

Significant factors in this quadrant highlight the areas designated for self-expression. Exhibits a self-motivated, self-oriented nature characterized by independently mapping out life and following an individual path, encountering difficulties only when impeded by external forces. Personal identity and resources form the basis for all further success. A robust sense of internal security is deemed essential prior to engaging with broader society. Exhibits a need for stability and a steady routine, favoring the familiar over change. Prioritizes harmony and peaceful surroundings, consistently seeking balance, especially during stressful times.
